message.body: Hey Stu, do you have any extra parking spots on N Champlain St? Ria and I don't have enough spots in our new driveway and would be willing to rent one. -Gabi
Hey Gabi. Unfortunately I don't have any extra. I'll keep my ears open though for spots. What's your address and how far are you willing to walk?
Go to Vt Paint and ask for David, the owner. He has spaces out back he rents. He just told me he has room
